<br>
BUT, if it was possible.  I'd say you go into the temple, pay (your_level * 100pp) to the church and receive the blessings of your new order.  It would create a money-sink, and be enough that people won't be changing all the time.<br>
<br>
If a high elf wished to worhip Innoruk for example, they would have done huge amounts of faction work in order to enter the city freely and approach the temple in the first place.  Once &quot;converted&quot; however, they would then be shuned in their own town I'm sure.<br>
